{"id":6364,"date":"2024-10-13T18:17:45","date_gmt":"2024-10-13T18:17:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gei.thomsuninfocare.com\/?p=6364"},"modified":"2025-01-16T11:41:32","modified_gmt":"2025-01-16T11:41:32","slug":"dr-juhy-cherian","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/dr-juhy-cherian\/","title":{"rendered":"Dr. Juhy Cherian"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-1 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"max-width:1414.4px;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-0 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-padding-top:40px;--awb-padding-bottom:50px;--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-1 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Educational Qualifications<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\"><p>Dr. Juhy Cherian holds an MS in Ophthalmology from the Pondicherry Institute of Medical Sciences, completed in 2017, and later earned a DNB in Ophthalmology in 2020. She also holds an MBBS degree from MOSC Medical College in Kolencherry, Kerala, completed in 2009. Dr. Cherian is registered with the Kerala State Medical Council, registration number 56864.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-2 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Specialisation<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-2\"><p>She specializes in medical retina and cataract, with expertise in general ophthalmic conditions and emergencies. Her procedural skills include Small Incision Cataract Surgery, Phacoemulsification, and Intravitreal injections, along with competence in both anterior and posterior segment lasers.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-3 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Work Experience<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-3\"><p>Senior Resident-Ophthalmology Pondicherry Institute of Medical Sciences, Pondicherry September 2020 to August 2021<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: var(--awb-text-color); font-family: var(--awb-text-font-family); font-size: var(--awb-font-size); font-style: var(--awb-text-font-style); font-weight: var(--awb-text-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--awb-letter-spacing); text-align: var(--awb-content-alignment); text-transform: var(--awb-text-transform); background-color: var(--awb-bg-color-hover);\">Medical retina-cum-Research fellow at Giridhar eye institute Kochi August 2021 to December 2021<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Cataract and medical retina fellow at Giridhar eye institute Kochi January 2022 to December 2022<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-4 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Course Attended<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-4\"><p>\u2022 One-month observership at Aravind Eye Hospital, Pondicherry.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Participated in Biostatics and Research Methodology Workshop conducted in Pondicherry institute of Medical Sciences on August 2017.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Leadership developmental programme by KSOS October 2023<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-5 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:none;\">Conferences &amp; CME Attended<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-5\"><p>\u2022 Update on Diabetic Retinopathy CME, JIPMER, Pondicherry in November 2019.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 SALEM EYECON, Tamil Nadu Ophthalmic Association, August 2019, Salem.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cCUTTING EDGE\u201919\u201d-Held at Aravind Eye Hospital, Pondicherry, July,2019.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 34th Asia-Pacific Academy of Ophthalmology (APAO) Congress Bangkok, Thailand, March 2019.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 AIOS-ARC Cataract and Glaucoma Symposium, February 2019 at JIPMER Pondicherry.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cNEURO CONNECT CME 2018\u201d- Held at Aravind Eye Hospital, Chennai, December 2018.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Southern Regional Ophthalmic Conference and 37th Annual Conference of Karnataka State Ophthalmic Society, December 2018 at A.J Institute of Medical Sciences and Research Centre, Mangalore.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Pudhuvue\u201918 &#8211; 66th Annual Conference of Tamil Nadu Ophthalmic Association, August 2018 at Mahatma Gandhi Medical College and Research Institute, Pondicherry.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 KSOS Drishti 2022 \u201349th Annual conference of KSOS held at Calicut<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-6 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:none;\">Presentations<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-6\"><p>\u2022 \u201cProfile of Glaucoma in a teaching hospital in Southern India\u201d-Presented at 34th APAO Bangkok, Thailand.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cOcular ischemia and Beyond: Ocular Ischemic Syndrome\u201d-Presented at 34th APAO Bangkok, Thailand.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cBlinding Mucor attacks with fervour-A case series\u201d-E-poster presentation at TNOA Pudhuvue 2018.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cA Key to the diagnosis: Papilledema to CVT in a case of Polycythemia\u201d-E-poster presented at SALEM EYECON, TNOA 2019.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cOcular ischemia and beyond-Ocular ischemic syndrome\u201d-E poster presented at SALEM EYECON, TNOA 2019.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cBurden of blindness due to glaucoma in a teaching hospital in Southern India\u201d-E poster SALEM EYECON, TNOA 2019.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cBlinding Mucor attacks with fervour-A case series\u201d-Presented a paper in 37th Karnataka State Ophthalmic Conference, Mangalore 2018.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cPost-operative Vision Loss following non ocular surgery-A Boon and Bane\u201d Presented in PIMS Scientific Society in August 2018.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: var(--awb-bg-color-hover); color: var(--awb-text-color); font-family: var(--awb-text-font-family); font-size: var(--awb-font-size); font-style: var(--awb-text-font-style); font-weight: var(--awb-text-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--awb-letter-spacing); text-align: var(--awb-content-alignment); text-transform: var(--awb-text-transform);\">\u2022 \u201cCase of Polycythemia presenting as Papilledema\u201d-Paper presented as part of Scientific Society Day events on 15th October 2019.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cEmmetropization after Phacoemulsification\u201d-Paper presented in TNOA Nov 2020<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cEfficacy of retropupillary iris claw IOL in correction of aphakia\u201d- Paper presented in KSOS Drishti 2022<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cPredominant peripheral lesions \u2013 a key finding in diabetic retinopathy\u201d- Paper presented in KSOS Drishti 2022<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 \u201cMyopic choroidal neovascular membrane\u201d \u2013 Myopia Conclave 2023<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-7 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:none;\">Achievements &amp; Honours<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-7\"><p>\u2022 Gold medalist Ophthalmology Pondicherry University 2020<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-8 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:none;\">Publications<\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-separator\" style=\"align-self: flex-start;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;max-width:20%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;--awb-sep-color:var(--awb-color4);border-color:var(--awb-color4);border-top-width:2px;\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-8\"><p>\u2022 Cherian, Juhy; Giridhar, Anantharaman; Sivaprasad, Sobha1; Rajalakshmi, R2; Raman, Rajiv3; Khan, Rehana4; Prakash, Nimmy; Rodrigues, Ann M. Predominant peripheral lesions in patients with diabetic retinopathy and its association with systemic comorbidities. Indian Journal of Ophthalmology 70(8):p 3021-3025, August 2022.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 PramodKumar TA, Sivaprasad S, Venkatesan U, Mohan V, Anjana RM, Unnikrishnan R, Cherian J, Giridhar A, Gopalakrishnan M, Rajalakshmi R. Role of cystatin C in the detection of sight-threatening diabetic retinopathy in Asian Indians with type 2 diabetes. J Diabetes Complications. 2023 Aug;37(8):108545.<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Asokan K, Cherian J, Vijay V, Prasanth HR, Srinivasan R. Multiple migratory caterpillar hairs in the eye \u2013 A case report. Indian J Clin Exp Ophthalmol 2022;8(4):559-562. \u2022 Cherian, Juhy; Giridhar, Anantharaman; Sivaprasad, Sobha1; Rajalakshmi, R2; Raman, Rajiv3; Khan, Rehana4; Prakash, Nimmy; Rodrigues, Ann M. Predominant peripheral lesions in patients with diabetic retinopathy and its association with systemic comorbidities. Indian Journal of Ophthalmology 70(8):p 3021-3025, August 2022<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Cherian J,Wadwekar B.Polycythemia rubra vera presenting as a case of papilledema.Indian J Opthalmol Case Rep 2021;1:776-8<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Kuriachan KE, George GS, Cherian J, et al. A cross-sectional study on the prevalence of self-medication practices and its associated factors among housewives in rural areas of Ernakulam district. J.Evolution Med.Dent.Sci 2016;5(46):2909-13.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-2 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling fusion-animated\" style=\"--awb-background-position:right center;--awb-border-sizes-top:0px;--awb-border-sizes-bottom:0px;--awb-border-sizes-left:0px;--awb-border-sizes-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-padding-top:30px;--awb-padding-right:30px;--awb-padding-bot